<div class="andf-cover">
<h1 class="andf-h andf-h1">Software Licence and Services Agreement</h1>
<p class="andf-cover-subtitle">Enterprise SaaS Agreement — Confidential</p>
<p class="andf-cover-authors">Legal Department</p>
<p class="andf-cover-date">2026-03-02</p>
<hr class="andf-cover-divider">
</div>
<p class="andf-p">This Software Licence and Services Agreement (the <strong>&quot;Agreement&quot;</strong>) is entered into as of <strong>1 March 2026</strong> (the <strong>&quot;Effective Date&quot;</strong>) by and between:</p>
<figure class="andf-table-wrap">
<table class="andf-table"><thead><tr>
<th style="text-align:left"></th>
<th style="text-align:left">Provider</th>
<th style="text-align:left">Customer</th>
</tr></thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:left">Legal name</td>
<td style="text-align:left">Acme Corporation Ltd</td>
<td style="text-align:left">Beta Technologies Ltd</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:left">Company no.</td>
<td style="text-align:left">12345678</td>
<td style="text-align:left">87654321</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:left">Registered address</td>
<td style="text-align:left">1 Tech Lane, London, EC1A 1AA</td>
<td style="text-align:left">50 High Street, Manchester, M1 1AD</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:left">Contact email</td>
<td style="text-align:left">legal@acme.example.com</td>
<td style="text-align:left">legal@beta.example.com</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table></figure>
<p class="andf-p">In this Agreement the following terms have the meanings set out below:</p>
<ul class="andf-list">
<li style="margin-left:0px"><strong>&quot;Software&quot;</strong> means Acme&#x27;s cloud-based platform known as AcmeSuite.</li>
<li style="margin-left:0px"><strong>&quot;Services&quot;</strong> means implementation, support, and maintenance services.</li>
<li style="margin-left:0px"><strong>&quot;Authorised Users&quot;</strong> means the Customer&#x27;s employees and contractors.</li>
<li style="margin-left:0px"><strong>&quot;Confidential Information&quot;</strong> means any non-public information disclosed.</li>
<li style="margin-left:0px"><strong>&quot;Personal Data&quot;</strong> has the meaning given in the UK GDPR.</li>
</ul>
<p class="andf-p">Subject to the terms of this Agreement and payment of all fees, Acme grants to the Customer a <strong>non-exclusive, non-transferable, revocable licence</strong> to access and use the Software during the Term solely for the Customer&#x27;s internal business purposes.</p>
<div class="andf-callout andf-callout-error"><div class="andf-callout-title">✖ Restrictions</div><p>The Customer must not: (a) sublicence or resell the Software; (b) reverse-engineer or decompile any part; (c) use the Software to develop a competing product; or (d) exceed the Authorised User limit specified in Schedule 1.</p></div>
<div class="andf-page-num">1</div>
</div>

<div class="andf-page" id="page-2">
<figure class="andf-table-wrap">
<figcaption class="andf-table-caption">Schedule 1: Fee Schedule</figcaption>
<table class="andf-table"><thead><tr>
<th style="text-align:left">Item</th>
<th style="text-align:right">Year 1</th>
<th style="text-align:right">Year 2</th>
<th style="text-align:right">Year 3</th>
</tr></thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:left">Licence fee</td>
<td style="text-align:right">$800,000</td>
<td style="text-align:right">$800,000</td>
<td style="text-align:right">$800,000</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:left">Implementation</td>
<td style="text-align:right">$150,000</td>
<td style="text-align:right">—</td>
<td style="text-align:right">—</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:left">Training</td>
<td style="text-align:right">$30,000</td>
<td style="text-align:right">$15,000</td>
<td style="text-align:right">$15,000</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:left">Support (24/7 Tier 1)</td>
<td style="text-align:right">Included</td>
<td style="text-align:right">Included</td>
<td style="text-align:right">Included</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:left"><strong>Annual total</strong></td>
<td style="text-align:right"><strong>$980,000</strong></td>
<td style="text-align:right"><strong>$815,000</strong></td>
<td style="text-align:right"><strong>$815,000</strong></td>
</tr>
</tbody></table></figure>
<p class="andf-p">All fees are payable within <strong>30 days</strong> of invoice date. Late payments accrue interest at 4% per annum above the Bank of England base rate.</p>
<p class="andf-p">Acme shall use commercially reasonable efforts to ensure the Software is available <strong>99.9% of each calendar month</strong> (&quot;Uptime SLA&quot;), excluding scheduled maintenance windows notified at least 48 hours in advance.</p>
